name: The State of Startup Funding in Egypt

description: Since 2011, a buzz started around building your own startup and several organizations and support mechanisms had been evolving since then, yet some observers are critically challenging the viability of the startup movement in Egypt.Funding is both a main challenge and an honest indicator of the leve…

data.message:
don't think so :)
check the details and you will figure out why

This event is run by Egypreneur - الريادي المصري. I know the group vaguely and those who live in Egypt in this group know it and know it's related to some good activities. So, even though not much details were available, I'm *thinking* it'll be a good opportunity to involve with other serious entrepreneurs in Egypt.
You may forward any questions or reservations you have to Abdelrahman Magdy by adding a comment here. By the way, I'm *not* affiliated in any way. Just trying to help.
Egypreneur has been around for a long time, they're well known in the startup community here and if they work out something, expect it to be good.
